imdb.plot outline: Annoying Orange isn't just an orange...he's also a gaming maniac. Watch as the prince of puns takes on your favorite video games while he tells jokes and tries to make you laugh. From mobile games to console, no game is safe from this silly citrus. You'll laugh. You'll cry laugh. You'll scream laugh. Laugher for everyone.
